Text: Only 4 downloads?  Looks like there weren't really that many people who had trouble finding TweakNT elsewhere.  I know I didn't; got it in minutes through eMule!

Or then again, it had been downloaded over a hundred times from an older torrent for this same program.

In any case, looking for it elsewhere such as through P2P is better since nobody is bothering to seed any of these tiny torrents.
